      "description": "This car is in mint condition. The exterior is free of scratches, dents, and paint imperfections, presenting a clean and unblemished appearance. The interior shows no signs of wear, with all surfaces, seating, and trim in like-new condition. Mechanically, the car is in excellent working order with no known issues.",
